---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About SlyTech Blog — homelab builds, cybersecurity lab work, and infrastructure projects."
  matrixOpacity={0.03}
>
  <div class="container" style="padding-top:3.5rem;padding-bottom:6rem;max-width:760px;">
    <div class="about-header">
      <span class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--color-accent);letter-spacing:0.1em;">ABOUT</span>
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2rem);font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-top:0.75rem;line-height:1.25;">
        SlyTech Blog
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        This is where I document my homelab builds, cybersecurity lab work, and infrastructure
        projects. Everything here is something I actually built and ran on real hardware.
      </p>

      <h2>What I'm building</h2>
      <p>
        My homelab runs on Proxmox with a dedicated cybersecurity lab server called Citadel.
        Current stack includes Wazuh for SIEM, Splunk for log analysis and detection engineering,
        pfSense for network segmentation, and a rotating set of VMs for whatever I'm working
        through that week. Every post here is something I actually built and ran.
      </p>

      <h2>Categories</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--cat-detection)">Detection</strong> — SIEM setups, detection rules, SOC workflows, MITRE ATT&CK mapping</li>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--cat-compliance)">Compliance</strong> — ISO 27001, NIST CSF, OpenSCAP, evidence collection</li>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--cat-homelab)">Homelab</strong> — Proxmox, networking, VMs, infrastructure</li>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--cat-cloud)">Cloud</strong> — Azure, cloud security, cloud-native labs</li>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--cat-iam)">IAM</strong> — Identity, access management, Active Directory</li>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--cat-career)">Career</strong> — Certs, learning paths, thoughts on breaking into cybersecurity</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Find me</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="https://github.com/SlyCyberLab" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/SlyCyberLab</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
</style>
